commit_message:
Added command line switches

Run "-s <MiRNA sequence>" to get a response directly
Run "-h" or "--help" to get usage information

If run without flags, will ask the user for input and wait for a keypress to quit.

Convert into module

Now can be imported as a module in addition to being run as a script.

Will wait for user interaction after giving the output in script mode, to allow the script to be run from a file explorer.
